div.p:
                        Object. Then we must not deny it to them
for every grosse sin neither; seeing you affirme,
that every grosse sinne breaketh not Covenant.

                        To the second Argument that the payment of
the same thing in the Obligation, leaveth no roome
for pardon he answereth thus:

div.head:
Sayings of excellent Divines;
added to satisfie you who charge
mee with Singularity.
